        <updateDate>2021-04-28T21:33:27Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Clarifying Law Around Insurance of Marijuana Act or the CLAIM Act </b></p> <p>This bill generally provides a safe harbor from penalties or other adverse agency action for insurance companies that provide services to cannabis-related legitimate businesses in jurisdictions where such activity is legal. </p> <p>The Government Accountability Office must report on barriers to marketplace entry for minority-owned and women-owned cannabis-related businesses. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
